

PetPro 🐶🐱

PetPro is an AI-powered web application designed to assist pet owners in managing their pets' needs efficiently. It offers an AI chatbot for guidance, diet recommendations, a vet locator, and an integrated shopping feature for pet-related products.

Features 🚀

AI Chatbot 🤖 – Get instant advice and answers about pet care.

Meal and Diet Planner 🥩 – Personalized meal plans for cats and dogs.

Vet Clinic Locator 📍 – Uses Google Maps to find the nearest vet clinics.

Pet Product Store 🛒 – Redirects to e-commerce platforms like  Amazon.


Tech Stack 🛠

Backend: Python (Django), Meta API (Groq AI integration)

Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript

Database: MongoDB (via Djongo)




Installation & Setup ⚙️

Prerequisites

Python 3.12 with django 

MongoDB installed and running




Steps to Run Locally

1. Clone the Repository

git clone https://github.com/23viv/petpro.git
cd petpro


2. Set Up Virtual Environment (Optional but Recommended)

python -m venv venv  
source venv/bin/activate  # On Windows use `venv\Scripts\activate`


3. Install Dependencies

pip install -r requirements.txt


4. Configure Database (MongoDB)
Update settings.py with your MongoDB connection details.


5. Run Migrations

python manage.py migrate


6. Start the Development Server

python manage.py runserver


7. Open in Browser
Visit http://127.0.0.1:8000/



Usage Guide 📝

Login / Signup – Register or log in to access features.

Chatbot – Type queries to get AI-generated pet advice.

Diet Planner – Enter pet details to receive meal suggestions.

Vet Finder – Locate nearby vet clinics via Google Maps.

Product Store – Browse and buy pet products through Amazon.


